title: Please Identify this font
content:
Does anyone know what is the font used here? TIA

author: Supernov

comments.content: I suspect this is a custom job…and a pretty poor one, at that. Not only do the ?M and /W not match the rest of the letters in style; they're also visible shorter than all of the other characters.
